<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15745</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比打开体育馆的门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15745</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森、尼娜和莉琪已经到了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20998</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师正在发吸汗带。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32654</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“雪莉老师，我们今天做什么？” 波比问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32654</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37746</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要锻炼。” 雪莉老师回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37746</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43441</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要打篮球吗？” 波比兴奋地问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43441</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47574</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要做一种不一样的锻炼。” 她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47574</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51504</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天我们要锻炼我们的大脑！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们互相看着对方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大脑？我们今天要做数学题吗？” 尼娜皱着眉头问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62084</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66126</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66126</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70665</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不是。我这里有一些脑筋急转弯。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70665</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师拿起一桶卡片。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78763</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“给你，尼娜。” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78763</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85177</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“选一张卡片在心里默读。然后选一个人来回答。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85177</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88956</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜选了一张卡片看了看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88956</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94480</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她笑了。“我选波比。” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94480</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99097</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太平洋的中间是什么？” 尼娜问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99097</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103612</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很简单，海水。” 波比回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103612</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111165</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜哈哈大笑。“不对，是 ‘平’。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111165</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117149</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>太-平-洋，中间是 ‘平’。明白了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117149</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123001</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她对雪莉老师笑了笑。“真好玩儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123001</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126048</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好了，波比，下一个是你。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126048</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129616</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>选一张卡片吧。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129616</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比选了一张卡片看了看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136162</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“贾森！” 他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136162</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140600</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么东西只会往上，不会往下？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140600</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145701</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森耸耸肩。“热气球？云？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145701</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149358</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“只能有一个答案！” 波比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149358</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151361</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧，云。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151361</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158138</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，是年龄！” 波比在贾森面前挥了挥卡片。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158138</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161463</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“轮到我了。” 贾森说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161463</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164455</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他从桶里选了一张卡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164455</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168424</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个问题不错。” 他对莉琪说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168424</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171850</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么东西在雨里不会变得更湿？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪想了想。“雨伞？” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182537</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，是水！” 贾森开心地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182537</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185827</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧，到我了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185827</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192397</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜，天气越热，爬得越高的东西是什么？” 莉琪问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192397</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199514</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太阳当空照……” 尼娜开始轻轻地唱起歌来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199514</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203241</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是太阳！” 她大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203241</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208688</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，答案是温度计。” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208688</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213376</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“雪莉老师，轮到您了！” 贾森说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213376</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216110</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好，开始了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216110</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222196</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师选了一张卡片，闭上眼睛，转了一圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222196</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227431</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当她停下来的时候，她正对着波比。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227431</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234017</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“波比。” 雪莉老师说，“什么布剪不断？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234017</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比想了想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242041</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么布剪不断？” 他重复着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242041</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248507</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“抹布、拖布、瀑布！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248507</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253804</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师，答案是瀑布！” 波比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253804</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256765</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师拍手笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256765</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263520</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“非常棒！” 她说，“你答对了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263520</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268161</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这些脑筋急转弯很难。” 尼娜说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268161</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270731</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的头都疼了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270731</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277278</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“雪莉老师，我可以把这些卡片带回家吗？” 波比问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277278</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285966</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要学会世上所有的脑筋急转弯！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>